data.description:
Welcome to this stunning custom 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasting an attached flex room with a convenient half bath, nestled on an expansive fenced corner lot. The open floor plan seamlessly integrates a gourmet kitchen featuring quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a spacious island—perfect for culinary enthusiasts and gatherings. Enjoy ample entertainment space highlighted by vaulted ceilings and a cozy fireplace. The primary bedroom offers a luxurious retreat with a separate soaking tub, shower, and an additional vanity area. This huge back yard also includes a shed.  Don't miss the chance to make this beautifully designed property your new home!
*Flex room does not show on the floor plan photo
